msgstr "Tilvalg for at sammenligne og sammenflette mapper"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1523
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The &kdiff3;-preferences (menu \"Settings\"-&gt;\"Configure &kdiff3;\") "
