msgstr "Mønster for filer:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1532
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Only files that match any pattern here will be put in the tree. More than "
#| "one pattern may be specified here by using the semicolon \";\" as "
